ReviewText:
i love margaritas - salty, limey goodness. i love philosophy shower gels - cleanses well, leaves my skin soft, doesn't strip or leave my skin greasy, and as vibrant as the scent is in the shower, it doesn't linger (because who wants to walk around smelling like food all day?).

and just like i was hoping, this is a perfect blend of two of my favorite things. :)

if you like margaritas, get this! you won't be disappointed. (and you can 'indulge' in the morning before work without actually drinking, haha!)
